codex
The public header confirms the guide is mostly on the right API surface, but a few phrases overstate application ownership and one example should guard `InvokeGlobalProc` because the template implementation calls the returned function object directly. I’m checking implementation behavior next so the edits reflect how add-ons are enumerated, loaded, and registered.
